Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
lead_paragraph: Sydney Carter hit the go-ahead free throws with 23 seconds left and defending champion Texas A&M fought off scrappy Arkansas, 61-59, in the second round of the Raleigh Regional.
